"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭文字D<br />\n人肉叉燒包<br />\n伊波拉病毒<br />\n三五成群</blockquote><br />\n三五成群點樣拍到續集呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e68a279bc5b314d7bbedb3302d99e5ee1d70053","tid":395443,"uid":1099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"龍咁威"},{"pid":"9af2bbea26487ca2989e00dd6e183ae116ace628","tid":395443,"uid":13107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:20:09.000Z","msg":"頭d"},{"pid":"1fdf0d9547117af48f0ed9bb1b0c5d612a0daa26","tid":395443,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暗戰<br />\n倚天屠龍記之魔教教主</blockquote><br />\n暗戰第二集係幾好睇，但已經開始hold唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ab391b9052a55057d8f510a82175e2a3120127","tid":395443,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5c262319981887a936e56a9a58fb8d9389e895","tid":395443,"uid":20707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"狂舞派"},{"pid":"47aef611ead24037196d9ada59d4a14962ddebd1","tid":395443,"uid":7192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常好睇既出續集多數係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c04ab70ea428cd4ed706d9b394cd8b19d0775f","tid":395443,"uid":59869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似教父咁出埋第三集<br />\n講廿年後古天樂想收山要搵人頂返個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後都係無啦啦出個飛機收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a384a703ee40c0f8dd8217567fa0dadd7ce14556","tid":395443,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似教父咁出埋第三集<br />\n講廿年後古天樂想收山要搵人頂返個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後都係無啦啦出個飛機收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20年太耐，10年差唔多，由當年計到而家差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n古天樂冇得收山嫁啦，上年要佢做一千年都要做。<br />\n<br />\n應該係佢想繼續做，但心裡又唔想做，最好已經有仔。<br />\n<br />\n最後字頭入面要篡位收佢皮，仲收埋佢全家皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86e0eb767229e259b90d6c578c1cc5903953bd4","tid":395443,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暗戰<br />\n倚天屠龍記之魔教教主</blockquote><br />\n廿幾年都未去到大都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b96bcfcabb0d8aee759fd4dda49c9aba4b45c28","tid":395443,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>倚天本來好似plan左係出三集<br />\n但票房食哂屎 所以有頭冇尾</blockquote><br />\n宜家都好難拍返出黎<br />\n<br />\n又洪金寶又李連杰 吳耀漢 張敏黎婆邱</blockquote><br />\n啲人咁老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbf20c83f3bfa6a01e586